; A Turing machine that decides the language L over the alphabet {0, 1} consisting
; of all strings with the same number of 0’s as 1’s.

; first occurrence of 0 or 1
0 0 x r a
0 1 x r b

; keep going if we don't find the other character
a 0 0 R a
a x x R a
b 1 1 R b
b x x R b

; if we make it to the end we reject
a _ _ r halt-reject
b _ _ r halt-reject

; go back
a 1 x l L
b 0 x l L

; accept if we blank out everything
0 _ _ l halt-accept
0 x x r 0

; go back
L x x l L
L 0 0 l L
L 1 1 l L
L _ _ r 0
